Texts.Chs: 厄休安龙人以一种弱很多的形式生产磷。优普利水会自然地与它一起生长。
Texts.Eng: Eld'uukhar grow Phosite in a much weaker form. Upilite naturally grows with it.

Texts.Chs: 这些晶体似乎只是相互生长。
Texts.Eng: These crystals seem to only grow with each other.

Texts.Chs: 优普利水晶只会与磷酸水晶一同生长，两者缺一不可。
Texts.Eng: Upilite only grows with Phosite, you can't have one without the other.
